        <briefdescription>
<para>Updates scale for all entities with dirty ScaleComponents. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For each entity with the required components, calculates the scale factor needed to resize the model from its original dimensions to the desired world-space dimensions.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
